[The report contains a table of cases reported, discarded, under investigation, confirmed, and deaths for the period 1 Jul 2017 to 6 Feb 2018. The confirmed cases are all in the Federal District and the states of Rio de Janeiro, São Paulo, and Minas Gerais. There are reported scattered cases in 23 other states. This is not surprising since this area is endemic for YF virus and a few cases occur sporadically. - Mod.TY

